          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Hebrew</add>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p><addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee>  As <persName>Mr
                                                  Marcusson</persName> has honored me,<lb/> with the
                                        reading of your letter, I wish<lb/> hereby to add, that I am
                                        surprised to<lb/> find, that from what you will have
                                        perceived<lb/> in my former letter, and which I was<lb/>
                                        sorry to find not printed, that the<lb/> words from such
                                        sources should have the least effect on any unprejudized
                                        mind.<lb/> As far as I have had the opportunity<lb/> to
                                        learn <persName>M. M.</persName> character, I am fully<lb/>
                                        convinced of the soundness of his princi<lb/>ples on
                                        Judaism, and from what I know<lb/> of the other parties I am
                                        certain<lb/> that they are liars who could forswear<lb/> for
                                        the sake of gain the living God of<lb/>
                                        <placeName>Israel</placeName>, that no reliance can be
                                        placed<lb/> on their assertions, and <sic>wherfore</sic>
                                        not<lb/> make them ashamed by a <sic>streight</sic><lb/>
                                        forward answer by saying we do not<lb/> believe you nor any
                                        mean apostate.<lb/> such are the sentiments of yours,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Sir Respectfully in haste</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">
                                        <persName role="author">L. Jaroslawski</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I will be in <placeName>Phila</placeName> next
                                        month.<lb/> at present for answering or publishing any of
                                        these matters<lb/> in your paper, I would best submit to
                                        your sound senses<lb/> and judgment why have they neglected
                                        so long responding?</p>
                    </body>
